snippet.textDisplay:
The emergence of Hagi, Aribo, Edmundson, Helander & Kamberi should have been seen as excellent progress from last year, but has been overshadowed of late by the unexpected loss of form of established stars. To say there was a lot riding on tonight's result is an understatement, but how the team responded.
We were treated to a tactical masterclass and a game plan executed by eleven warriors. Delighted that Ryan Kent got the goal and hope it will give him the confidence to go on and show people how good he is.
Absolutely buzzing.
